reviewText:
If you're looking for Zombie Survival game go look somewhere else because this game is just an arcade with shooter with survival elements (hunger; sleep; thisty) and they not make the game challenging at all.
In fact the real challenge on this game is dealing with Zombie hordes while having to use the clumsy controls it has.

Just try it if can get this game by US $ 5,00 (R$ 10,00) otherwise skip it.

Good:
- Dynamic Lightning and Day/Night cycling;
- Crafting (not much complex);
- Kovac NPC;
- Zombie violence;

Bad:
- Clumsy controls and ridiculous attack animations;
- Not survival at all;
- Real bad voice acting;
- The fire element in this game is awful;
